        },
        "statistical_analysis": "All experiments repeated three times except in vitro dissolution (six times). Data expressed as mean ± SD. p < 0.05 considered significant. Similarity factor f2 calculated using equation: f2 = 50 * log{[1 + (1/n)Σ(Rt-Tt)^2]^{-0.5} * 100}.",
